title: Continuum Magazine #1 : Paranormal, UFOs, Ghosts, Occult
description:
We are a growing magazine with detailed colorful articles on UFOs and Ghosts and the Occult and many other topics. We are based from the paranormal community forum Mabus Incarnate. We have interviewed such greats as William Birnes from UFO Hunters off the History Channel and many more. That transcript is included in the first issue. We are also looking for members for our community to come discuss and debate on our forum. New writers wanted for our magazine. Hope to see you there. 

www.mabusincarnate.com
